import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1):
    v0 = jnp.add(x0, x0)
    v1 = jnp.cos(v0)
    v2 = jnp.minimum(v0, x1)
    v3 = jnp.cos(v1)
    v4 = jnp.sin(x0)
    v5 = jnp.subtract(v2, v4)
    v6 = jnp.exp(v4)
    v7 = jnp.maximum(v5, v5)
    v8 = jnp.maximum(x0, v6)
    v9 = jnp.maximum(v8, x0)
    return v9
